script.name: plugin.guilds.wbrowser.data
script.description: Guilds: Weapons Browser, get table data
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
$data = table alloc
$short.name = table alloc $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4017 $short.name['name'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=54 id=11 $short.name['laser'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=54 id=12 $short.name['missile'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=24 $short.name['range'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9510 $short.name['price'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3304 $short.name['reload'] = $read.text $short.name['spacer'] = ' ' $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=58 $short.name['races'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3305 $short.name['hull.damage'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3307 $short.name['hull.damage.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3306 $short.name['hull.damage.oos'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3308 $short.name['hull.damage.oos.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3309 $short.name['shield.damage'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3311 $short.name['shield.damage.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3310 $short.name['shield.damage.oos'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3312 $short.name['shield.damage.oos.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3313 $short.name['ammo'] = $read.text $short.name['has.ammo'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=30 $short.name['speed'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104422 $short.name['energy'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3314 $short.name['consumption'] = $read.text
$long.name = table alloc $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=22 $long.name['price'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=27 $long.name['reload'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=26 $long.name['hull.damage'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=98 $long.name['hull.damage.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=100 $long.name['hull.damage.oos'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=25 $long.name['shield.damage'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=97 $long.name['shield.damage.sec'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=99 $long.name['shield.damage.oos'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3315 $long.name['has.ammo'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=29 $long.name['ammo'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3317 $long.name['speed'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=31 $long.name['energy'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=32 $long.name['consumption'] = $read.text
$length = table alloc $length['name'] = 250 $length['laser'] = 250 $length['range'] = 50 $length['price'] = 80 $length['reload'] = 80 $length['spacer'] = 10 $length['races'] = 120 $length['hull.damage'] = 60 $length['hull.damage.sec'] = 60 $length['hull.damage.oos'] = 65 $length['hull.damage.oos.sec'] = 70 $length['shield.damage'] = 60 $length['shield.damage.sec'] = 60 $length['shield.damage.oos'] = 65 $length['shield.damage.oos.sec'] = 70 $length['has.ammo'] = 40 $length['ammo'] = 200 $length['speed'] = 60 $length['energy'] = 60 $length['consumption'] = 60
$is.right = table alloc $is.right['range'] = [TRUE] $is.right['price'] = [TRUE] $is.right['reload'] = [TRUE] $is.right['hull.damage'] = [TRUE] $is.right['hull.damage.sec'] = [TRUE] $is.right['hull.damage.oos'] = [TRUE] $is.right['hull.damage.oos.sec'] = [TRUE] $is.right['shield.damage'] = [TRUE] $is.right['shield.damage.sec'] = [TRUE] $is.right['shield.damage.oos'] = [TRUE] $is.right['shield.damage.oos.sec'] = [TRUE] $is.right['has.ammo'] = [TRUE] $is.right['speed'] = [TRUE] $is.right['consumption'] = [TRUE] $is.right['energy'] = [TRUE]
$no.sort = table alloc $no.sort['spacer'] = [TRUE] $no.sort['races'] = [TRUE]
$pages = table alloc $page = create new array, size=11, elements='laser', 'range', 'hull.damage.sec', 'shield.damage.sec', 'speed', 'energy', 'consumption', 'price' $page[8] = 'has.ammo' $page[9] = 'spacer' $page[10] = 'races' $pages['general'] = $page
$page.names = table alloc
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3302 $page.names['general'] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3303 $page.names['damage'] = $read.text
$page = create new array, size=9, elements='laser', 'hull.damage', 'hull.damage.sec', 'hull.damage.oos', 'shield.damage', 'shield.damage.sec', 'shield.damage.oos', 'spacer' $page[8] = 'ammo' $pages['damage'] = $page
$data['short.name'] = $short.name $data['right'] = $is.right $data['long.name'] = $long.name $data['length'] = $length $data['no.sort'] = $no.sort $data['pages'] = $pages $data['page.names'] = $page.names
return $data

sval.val: Guilds: Weapons Browser, get table data
